snippet.title: Best VGM 1657 - Super Mario Sunshine - Bianco Hills
snippet.description:
See also:

Best VGM 741 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s_Z71tcVVVg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

GameCube
Super Mario Sunshine (2002)
Bianco Hills
Koji Kondo & Shinobu Tanaka
